text: Every Sunday I am here to worship God.. With my sister's in Christ, and also the people here are friendly and helpful you will feel the happiness within them. And all race's are welcome anytime to visit this Place.
If you want to experience a solemn and peaceful worship with love and care from all member then visit this place if your staying in singapore.
A place where a culture of Christ is propagated!
Amazing and love hearing the words of God.
